%spark.pyspark
rm = spark.read.csv("s3://project-aaar/new_data/part-00000-f226c182-aa39-44df-a7fb-09b7ade36889-c000.csv", header = True)
rm2 = rm

%spark.pyspark
rm.dtypes

%spark.pyspark
rm.describe("age","day_of_week_of_death").show()

%spark.pyspark
rm.describe(["day_of_week_of_death"]).show()

%spark.pyspark
rm.crosstab('manner_of_death', 'sex').show()

%spark.pyspark
rm.crosstab('marital_status', 'sex').show()

%spark.pyspark
rm.groupby('manner_of_death').agg({'age': 'mean'}).show()

%spark.pyspark
rm.groupBy("method_of_disposition").count().show()

%spark.pyspark
rm.select('manner_of_death').distinct().rdd.map(lambda r: r[0]).collect()

%spark.pyspark
rm.registerTempTable("stats")

%spark.pyspark
df=(spark.sql("""
  SELECT CAST(month_of_death AS int), COUNT(month_of_death) as number_of_deaths
  FROM stats
  GROUP BY 1
  ORDER BY 1
"""))
z.show(df)

%spark.pyspark
death_age_manner=spark.sql(""" SELECT 
                CASE WHEN CAST(age AS float) > 900 THEN "75+" 
                WHEN CAST(age AS float) > 720 THEN "60-75" 
                WHEN CAST(age AS float) > 600 THEN "50-60" 
                WHEN CAST(age AS float) > 480 THEN "40-50" 
                WHEN CAST(age AS float) > 360 THEN "30-40" 
                WHEN CAST(age AS float) > 240 THEN "20-30" 
                WHEN CAST(age AS float) > 120 THEN "10-20" 
                ELSE "0-10" END AS Age_Group, 
                CASE WHEN manner_of_death = 1 THEN 'Accident' 
                WHEN manner_of_death = 2 THEN 'Suicide' 
                WHEN manner_of_death = 3 THEN 'Homicide' 
                WHEN manner_of_death = 6 THEN 'Self-Inflicted' 
                WHEN manner_of_death = 7 THEN 'Natural' 
                ELSE 'Other' END AS manner_of_death_new,
                place_of_injury_for_causes_w00_y34_except_y06_and_y07_,
                COUNT(1) 
            FROM stats 
            WHERE manner_of_death <> 7 AND place_of_injury_for_causes_w00_y34_except_y06_and_y07_ IS NOT NULL
            GROUP BY 1, 2, 3
            ORDER BY 1, 3 """)
z.show(death_age_manner)
